INSERT INTO `locales_page_text` VALUES (50666, 'Our lady is ready to act. Soon our humiliating defeat shall be overturned and our revenge will fall upon the mortals. You have a part to play in this. Muster your forces, you will strike against the Elves alongside the forces in the south. Your diversion is crucial to the plans of the lady. Some of the main host will be dispatched to you as well from the aperture. Do not fail, you know what the price for failure is.', NULL, NULL, NULL, '我们的女士已经准备好行动了。 很快我们的耻辱性失败就会被推翻，我们的复仇将落在凡人身上。 你有责任参与其中。 集结你的军队，你将与南方的军队一起对抗精灵。 你的转移对这位女士的计划至关重要。 一些主要宿主也会从光圈被派遣到你身边。 不要失败，你知道失败的代价是什么。', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO `locales_page_text` VALUES (3456, 'Transfering supplies to Icepoint Rock 09.04 05:31-10:50\n\n13.04 05:12-09:20 Established base at Icepoint Rock north of Winterspring\n\nRecon over Winterspring 18.04 20:03-22:14\n\nFlight to Icepoint Rock 03.05 06:04-', NULL, NULL, NULL, '将物资转移到冰点岩石 09.04 05:31-10:50\r\n\r\n13.04 05:12-09:20 在冬泉谷以北的冰点岩建立基地\r\n\r\n冬泉谷侦察 18.04 20:03-22:14\r\n\r\n飞往冰点岩 03.05 06:04-', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO `locales_page_text` VALUES (2825, 'The Grave of Admiral Caelan\n\nNever was there an Admiral so brave, who led his men with respect, dignity and honor.\n\nThe Kingdom of Kul Tiras weeps and so to do his brave crew.\n\n The Fleet will never forget you.', NULL, NULL, NULL, '凯兰海军上将之墓\r\n\r\n从来没有一位海军上将如此勇敢，他以尊重、尊严和荣誉的态度领导着他的部下。\r\n\r\n库尔提拉斯王国在哭泣，他勇敢的船员们也在哭泣。\r\n\r\n  舰队永远不会忘记你。', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO `locales_page_text` VALUES (50661, 'Centuries ago, the first Tauren tribes settled in the fertile lands of Multhan, harmonizing with the wild and untamed forces of nature, much like our own kind. These noble beings, though initially unrefined, held a deep reverence for nature akin to our own. The teachings of our druids bestowed upon them the knowledge of agriculture, animal husbandry, and even the written word.$B$BTheir spiritual devotion extended beyond their own traditions, embracing Cenarius, and Elune. Thus, an alliance was formed, fostering mutual growth and prosperity. Though occasional misunderstandings marred the harmony, the Kaldorei and the Tauren dwelt together in peace.', NULL, NULL, NULL, '几个世纪前，第一批牛头人部落定居在穆尔森的肥沃土地上，与我们自己的同类一样，与狂野和未驯服的自然力量和谐相处。 这些高贵的生物虽然最初未经雕琢，但与我们一样对自然抱有深深的敬畏。 我们德鲁伊的教义赋予了他们农业、畜牧业甚至文字的知识。$B$B他们的精神奉献超出了他们自己的传统，拥抱了塞纳留斯和艾露恩。 因此，联盟成立，促进共同发展和繁荣。 尽管偶尔会有误解破坏和谐，但卡多雷和牛头人和平相处。', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO `locales_page_text` VALUES (50662, 'However, the course of history took a fateful turn with the arrival of the Centaur clans from Morerume, now known as Desolace. These merciless forces launched a relentless assault upon the Tauren, seeking to dispossess them of their bountiful plains and banish them to desolate wastelands.$B$BThe brave Tauren fought valiantly against overwhelming odds, but the tide of battle turned against them. Day after day, they were relentlessly pushed eastward, closer to the precipice of despair.', NULL, NULL, NULL, '然而，随着半人马部族从莫雷鲁姆（现在被称为凄凉之地）的到来，历史的进程发生了致命的转变。 这些无情的军队对牛头人发起了无情的攻击，试图剥夺他们肥沃的平原，并将他们驱逐到荒凉的荒地。$B$B勇敢的牛头人在压倒性的优势下英勇作战，但战势却对他们不利。 日复一日，他们被无情地推向东方，逼近绝望的悬崖。', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO `locales_page_text` VALUES (50663, 'In a moment of solidarity, the Sentinel Army emerged to lend their aid in defense of their Tauren allies. United, they stood resolute, prepared to confront this formidable adversary.$B$BAlas, the true extent of the Centaur\'s ferocity caught the Sentinels off guard. Swift and merciless, the Centaur\'s style of warfare on open fields rendered the Sentinels\' customary ambush and hit-and-run tactics ineffective. Countless brave sisters fell, their sacrifice forever mourned.', NULL, NULL, NULL, '在团结一致的时刻，哨兵军团挺身而出，为保卫牛头人盟友提供援助。 团结起来，他们坚定不移，准备对抗这个强大的对手。$B$BAlas，半人马的真正凶猛程度让哨兵们措手不及。 半人马在开阔场地上的作战方式迅速而无情，使得哨兵惯用的伏击和打了就跑的战术变得无效。 无数勇敢的姐妹倒下，她们的牺牲永远为人们哀悼。', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO `locales_page_text` VALUES (50664, 'Amidst this dire situation, Shandris Feathermoon, burdened with a heavy heart, made the difficult decision to order a strategic retreat. The Sentinels regrouped within the familiar embrace of Ashenvale, leaving the Tauren to face their harrowing fate alone.$B$BUltimately, the Tauren lost their ancestral homeland, consigned to roam the desolate wastes of the East, forever marked by the curse of their displacement.', NULL, NULL, NULL, '在这种严峻的形势下，珊蒂斯羽月心情沉重，做出了艰难的决定，下令战略撤退。 哨兵们在灰谷熟悉的怀抱中重新集结，留下牛头人独自面对他们悲惨的命运。$B$B最终，牛头人失去了他们祖先的家园，被迫在东部荒凉的荒原上漫游，永远带着流离失所的诅咒。 。', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO `locales_page_text` VALUES (50665, 'This grievous chapter in our shared history serves as a testament to our deepest shame, a betrayal of our noble allies driven by the fear of losing more lives. Indeed, we may have preserved our own existence, but at what cost to our honor and integrity?', NULL, NULL, NULL, '我们共同历史上的这一悲惨篇章证明了我们最深的耻辱，是出于对失去更多生命的恐惧而背叛了我们的崇高盟友。 事实上，我们可能保住了自己的存在，但是我们的荣誉和正直付出了怎样的代价呢？', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO `locales_page_text` VALUES (50667, 'It is hereby directed that the dissemination of news pertaining to Isiden Perenolde\'s escape must be strictly controlled and confined. We must ensure that Mortimer and Celia Harlow remain entirely oblivious to his current status. They are to be led to believe that Isiden Perenolde continues to be incarcerated within the confines of the Dryrock Pit.$B$BHowever, let it be known that our intelligence suggests a different narrative. We strongly suspect that Isiden\'s escape was orchestrated by loyalists hailing from Alterac. We posit that he might have sought refuge and seclusion in the remote and desolate island of Tol Barad.', NULL, NULL, NULL, '特此指示，必须严格控制和限制有关伊西登·佩雷诺德越狱消息的传播。 我们必须确保莫蒂默和西莉亚·哈洛完全不知道他目前的身份。 他们将被引导相信伊西登·佩雷诺德继续被监禁在干岩坑的范围内。$B$B然而，让我们知道，我们的情报表明了不同的说法。 我们强烈怀疑艾西登的逃跑是由来自奥特兰克的忠诚者精心策划的。 我们推测他可能在偏远荒凉的托尔巴拉德岛寻求庇护和隐居。', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO `locales_page_text` VALUES (50668, 'In response to these developments, a search party was dispatched to investigate and locate Isiden Perenolde\'s whereabouts. Regrettably, we have yet to receive any communication or reports from the searching party, and their status remains unknown.$B$BAs we navigate this web of events, we urge utmost discretion and caution in handling this sensitive information. The repercussions of any inadvertent leaks could prove detrimental to the broader political landscape and the stability of our realm.$B$BAuthorized by:$B$BOsmark Dryrock.', NULL, NULL, NULL, '针对这些事态发展，一支搜寻队被派去调查并寻找伊西登·佩雷诺德的下落。 遗憾的是，我们尚未收到搜索方的任何通信或报告，其状态仍未知。$B$BA在我们浏览这一事件网络时，我们敦促在处理这些敏感信息时尽最大的谨慎和谨慎。 任何无意泄露的后果都可能对更广泛的政治格局和我们领域的稳定造成损害。$B$B授权者：$B$BOsmark Dryrock。', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO `locales_page_text` VALUES (50669, 'Had I not seen it with my own two eyes, I would have never understood just how fragile these mortals can be. My brother and I were tasked by our father to watch over this filthy kingdom. Courtiers at the keep of Greymane, sent by Lord Prestor— an influential voice in the Kingdom of Alterac —my brother and I quickly forced ourselves into the ranks of trusted nobles, reaching the ear of the King.$B$BIt is then that we began to slowly poison his mind with thoughts of rebellion, creating distress between him and his own people. Foolish humans, they could never have understood the weight of their own actions.', NULL, NULL, NULL, '如果不是我亲眼所见，我永远不会明白这些凡人是多么脆弱。 我和我的兄弟奉父亲之命看守这个肮脏的王国。 格雷迈恩要塞的朝臣们，是由普雷斯托勋爵——奥特兰克王国中一个有影响力的声音——派来的，我和我的兄弟很快就迫使自己进入了值得信赖的贵族行列，到达了国王的耳中。$B$B就在那时，我们 叛逆的思想开始慢慢毒害他的思想，在他和他自己的人民之间制造痛苦。 愚蠢的人类，他们永远无法理解自己行为的重要性。', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO `locales_page_text` VALUES (50670, 'After we turned Genn against his most trusted man, killing his wife in the process, the King became so depressed that a mere touch and a kind word was all it took to have him wrapped around my finger. During that time, there wasn\'t much in the works aside from the rebellion—save for the time we imprisoned the children of our so-called sovereign and told him they\'d faced a terrible death. They were lost at sea, thanks to the foolish Perenolde, whom Genn allowed into his kingdom — or so we told him.$B$BThe King became so dependent on me that I had him retreating to his chambers, allowing Gilneas to be in the capable hands of my brother and me.', NULL, NULL, NULL, '当我们让吉恩与他最信任的人为敌，并在此过程中杀死了他的妻子后，国王变得非常沮丧，只需要轻轻一碰和一句善意的话语就可以让他缠住我的手指。 在那段时间里，除了叛乱之外，没有什么进展——除了我们监禁所谓君主的孩子们并告诉他他们面临着可怕的死亡的那段时间。 他们在海上迷路了，多亏了愚蠢的佩瑞诺德，吉恩允许他进入他的王国——至少我们是这么告诉他的。$B$B国王变得如此依赖我，以至于我让他撤退到他的房间，让吉尔尼斯在 我和我兄弟的一双能干的手。', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO `locales_page_text` VALUES (50671, 'Alas, we had met our goal, but no word ever came from our father. Where was he? We had completed our goal—took over the country and slowly made it rot from the inside out. And so we waited, and waited, and waited some more. Many events occurred while we kept isolated in the city. My foolish brother even began to lavish in the desires of mortals, while I was responsible for keeping our King—happily insane and under our control, that is. Convinced that our father abandoned his plan, Mortimer decided he enjoyed this life too much, regardless of whether our father returned or not, and so we both decided to keep on living here and claim this place as our nest.', NULL, NULL, NULL, '唉，我们已经达到了目标，但父亲却没有任何消息。 他在哪儿？ 我们已经完成了我们的目标——接管这个国家并慢慢地让它从内到外腐烂。 所以我们等啊等，再等。 当我们被隔离在城市时，发生了很多事情。 我愚蠢的兄弟甚至开始在凡人的欲望中挥霍，而我则负责维持我们的国王——幸运的是，他疯了，并在我们的控制之下。 莫蒂默确信我们的父亲放弃了他的计划，他觉得无论我们的父亲是否回来，他都太享受这种生活了，所以我们都决定继续住在这里，并把这里当作我们的巢。', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO `locales_page_text` VALUES (50672, 'At one point, however, we still felt the need for leadership. Each day I would see the King depend on me for instructions and guidance—he clearly had no intention of making any more decisions by himself. At that moment, I felt jealous—a fit of jealousy overcame me. He was so codependent, yet at the same time, his thirst for direction was exactly what I myself was missing. Why would our father abandon us? Where would I even begin to find more supervision? How could I even trust such a thing?', NULL, NULL, NULL, '然而，在某一时刻，我们仍然感到需要领导力。 每天我都会看到国王依赖我的指示和指导——他显然无意再自己做出任何决定。 那一刻，我感到嫉妒——一阵嫉妒袭上心头。 他是如此的相互依赖，但与此同时，他对指导的渴望正是我自己所缺少的。 为什么我们的父亲要抛弃我们？ 我该从哪里开始寻找更多的监督呢？ 我怎么能相信这样的事情呢？', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO `locales_page_text` VALUES (50673, 'Fate decided for me, however. It came at night, growling and inhaling the air of the room as if it already belonged to him. At the sight of a hideous creature— a Worgen who crawled upon the walls and came from the Silverpine Forest, he called himself Father Lycan, a sentient being clad in tattered robes, covered in muck and blood. He claimed to be a preacher of blood who had pierced the veil between his world and ours so that we too could enjoy the gifts he had brought us.', NULL, NULL, NULL, '然而，命运为我做了决定。 它在晚上到来，咆哮着，吸入房间里的空气，仿佛房间已经属于他了。 当看到一个可怕的生物——一个从银松森林爬到墙上的狼人时，他称自己为狼人神父，一个穿着破烂长袍、浑身是淤泥和血的有知觉的生物。 他自称是一位血的传教士，刺破了他的世界和我们的世界之间的面纱，以便我们也能享受他带给我们的礼物。', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO `locales_page_text` VALUES (50674, 'It was through the seed of greed, and the foolish actions of the fanatical mage Ur and his self-called apprentice Arugal—who summoned the Worgen to Azeroth—that a horrible creature like Father Lycan was able to step foot on our land. He told us that the Worgen that had entered Azeroth before him were mere sentries, feral and mindless foot soldiers that only dictated that, one day, this land may be worthy enough to be blessed through conquest.', NULL, NULL, NULL, '正是通过贪婪的种子，以及狂热法师乌尔和他自称的学徒阿鲁高（将狼人召唤到艾泽拉斯）的愚蠢行为，像狼神父这样的可怕生物才能够踏上我们的土地。 他告诉我们，在他之前进入艾泽拉斯的狼人只是哨兵，是野蛮而盲目的步兵，他们只是表明，有一天，这片土地可能值得通过征服而受到祝福。', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO `locales_page_text` VALUES (50675, 'While at first the one who called himself a pricolich was someone I wish I had never encountered, I soon discovered the sheer amount of power that this creature possessed—as well as how beneficial it would be for me and my brother to ally ourselves with him. And through his teaching, we found new purpose, new guidance, and new instructions. We slowly corrupted the nobles, the guards, and even the King to consume raw flesh and blood, making them stronger and more addicted than ever before. The truth is, there is no other mortal race that would go so far to survive as these humans would.', NULL, NULL, NULL, '虽然一开始我希望自己从未遇到过那个自称为普里科利希的人，但我很快就发现了这个生物拥有的巨大力量，以及与他结盟对我和我的兄弟有多么有利 。 通过他的教导，我们找到了新的目的、新的指导和新的指示。 我们慢慢地腐化了贵族、守卫，甚至国王来消耗生肉和血肉，使他们比以往任何时候都更强大、更沉迷。 事实是，没有任何其他凡人种族能够像这些人类一样为了生存而走得那么远。', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO `locales_page_text` VALUES (50676, 'The humans have no real conviction. Treating the common folk like cattle, kidnapping and serving them on platters. Frankly, I was proud of my own accomplishments. To twist the beloved King of these men who still wish to see him on the throne. Still holding hope that he\'s merely ill or captured by us—the root of all evil—while he himself betrayed them.', NULL, NULL, NULL, '人类没有真正的信念。 把老百姓当作牛一样对待，把他们绑架并盛在盘子里。 坦白说，我为自己的成就感到自豪。 扭曲这些仍然希望看到他登上王位的人所敬爱的国王。 仍然抱有希望，认为他只是生病了或者被我们俘虏了——万恶之源——而他自己却背叛了他们。', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO `locales_page_text` VALUES (50677, 'I have heard you finally left your boring life behind and decided to serve the cause of the Alliance. Who would have imagined you\'d pick up a crossbow and claim yourself to be a hunter? It certainly reminds me of the days I first began my journey.$B$BYou will need proper guidance and a steady hand! You will find me behind the Abbey, next to the stables; be prepared.$B$BOld Jonah.', NULL, NULL, NULL, '我听说你终于摆脱了无聊的生活并决定为联盟的事业服务。 谁会想到你会拿起十字弓并声称自己是一名猎人？ 这确实让我想起了我第一次开始旅程的日子。$B$B你需要适当的指导和稳定的手！ 你会在修道院后面、马厩旁边找到我； 做好准备。$B$BO老乔纳。', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO `locales_page_text` VALUES (50678, 'Me bothers not writing too much here mon. Zol\'majin sends I from Revantusk Village to be teaching the youngins about the Fel magic. If you not be dead as you be reading this, it means you have the talent to summon the will of the Twisting Nether at your own fingertips.$B$BBut be careful mon, felfire burns worse than normal fire! Me be resting in this cave they be calling a Den — next to some other warlock that seems to have a weird syndrome, he believes himself to be some chosen one. Me be hoping you not be as boring as he.$B$B<The rest of the page is covered with a drawing that symbolizes a big-headed orc.', NULL, NULL, NULL, '我不想在这里写太多。 佐尔马金派我从恶牙村来教导年轻人邪能魔法。 如果你在阅读本文时没有死，这意味着你有能力在自己的指尖召唤扭曲虚空的意志。$B$B但是要小心，伙计，邪火比普通火燃烧得更厉害！ 我正在这个他们称之为巢穴的山洞里休息——旁边还有其他一些似乎患有奇怪综合症的术士，他相信自己是某个被选中的人。 我希望你不要像他一样无聊。$B$B<页面的其余部分覆盖着象征大头兽人的图画。', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO `locales_page_text` VALUES (10032, 'Due to excessive regulations recently introduced by the Stormwind City treasury, Shell Co has been forced to relocate its offices to the free trade port of Booty Bay.\r\n\r\nIf you are displeased by this development, please express your feelings to the visionless bureaucrats at Stormwind Keep that have conspired to keep you from attaining the wealth you deserve!', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO `locales_page_text` VALUES (50684, 'Wine was a true warlock. Beneath the dark exterior laid the most genuine person we\'ve met. Warlock chat will never be the same without him.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO `locales_page_text` VALUES (50685, 'It was an honor to have Gallifrey in guild, to teach her all about the game and regard her as a friend. May you ride your white wolf forever!', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO `locales_page_text` VALUES (50686, 'The loss of the Sunwell has affected us all, some more profoundly than others. Our daily use of the arcane has been curtailed. Unfortunately, some individuals have miscalculated the severity of the situation and have now fallen prey to their hunger, transforming into the withered.$B$BAs a promising mage apprentice, times may prove to be quite challenging for you. With the arcane being your primary source of power, you must possess the control and discipline to comprehend your limitations. Seek me out on the lower level of the main building, where our journey together can commence.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO `locales_page_text` VALUES (50687, 'Light be with you, aspirant. I am Lor\'thas, a Paladin, like yourself. I write this letter to inform you of my presence in the academy and to offer you advice and training. You are surely aware of our new condition that, sadly, cannot be prevented. However, we may prolong its inevitable onset.$B$BThe Light offers us discipline and salvation, though what we truly seek is redemption and justice. Under its brightness, the Light shall provide us a chance to repay the Scourge a debt long overdue. You shall find me on the lower level of the main building.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO `locales_page_text` VALUES (50688, 'Blessings of the Sun.$B$BI am pleased to learn that another devotee of faith has joined our cause. Many of our people were not previously eager to embrace the Light, even before the Scourge\'s attack. Some believers even abandoned their faith after the loss of our homeland.$B$BNonetheless, the Light\'s smallest glimmer shines even in the darkest cave. Thus, you and I are tasked with guiding our people back to their faith and helping them through these times of adversity. Though the Sunwell is gone, the Sun continues to shine brightly. Don\'t forget we are here to aid, heal, and support our people, which is precisely what they need now. If you seek my guidance or instruction, you shall locate me on the lower level of the main building.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO `locales_page_text` VALUES (50689, 'Thief, scoundrel, and outlaw: these names defined you before the fall of your homeland.$B$BIt seems that fate smiles upon you, for no one shall concern themselves with your past if you are willing to contribute to the greater cause. But I, who remember you, am interested in your change of heart.$B$BFear not, for my anger has subsided, and I am interested in your ability to endure the darkest aspects of Silvermoon. Join me, and together let us embrace these shadows, for you will never be wealthy, but your hunger will never again consume you.$B$BYou will find me to the left of the Golden Ranger.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO `locales_page_text` VALUES (50690, 'Anger can become your most powerful weapon as long as you do not let it eat away at you. Despite our losses, do you not perceive that many of the others have simply accepted their despair instead of channeling their willpower to reclaim and avenge?$B$BMy blade swirls with grace and poise, akin to how the leaves dance amid autumn. So too shall yours, if you join me for a lesson or two in mastering it. Perceive your anger as a tool. Tame it so that those who perish at your hands will be awed by your craft. I will be waiting for you in the smaller building to the left of the Golden Ranger.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO `locales_page_text` VALUES (50691, 'I greet you, fellow ranger-in-training. I appreciate the way you carry yourself and the determination you demonstrate in following the footsteps of our renowned brethren.$B$BBefore the fall of Quel\'Thalas, I was a freshly inducted member of the Farstriders, a contingent of skilled rangers who ventured beyond our borders to guard our lands and honor. The legacy of the Farstriders has been diminished during these trying times. However, I believe we can restore it, albeit gradually, together. Meet with me; I will be somewhere in the outskirts of Brinthilien.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO `locales_page_text` VALUES (50692, 'Destroy this letter once you have memorized its contents.$B$BAll preparations have been made. Send your delegation to Alah\'Thalas at once. Eldin is not an option; he will be recognized. Choose one of your most trusted men, and ensure they cover their eyes during the journey. $B$BI will await your arrival until tomorrow. Should you be delayed or unable to reach Alah\'Thalas in time, I will contact him independently. I trust in the best outcome.$B$BRommath', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO `locales_page_text` VALUES (50693, 'To the fallen of Quel\'Thalas, whose courage faced death unflinchingly, we pledge eternal honor. May the radiant embrace of the Eternal Sun guide your journey beyond, where your valor echoes among the stars. Your legacy, woven into the fabric of time, remains an undying flame in our hearts. In twilight\'s embrace, we declare that the fallen of Quel\'Thalas shall forever be remembered for their unyielding spirit and sacrifice.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO `locales_page_text` VALUES (50694, 'We are united under one home by the sacrifices of our brothers in arms.$B$BMay we always have this city to call our hearth, even in the darkest days. Shall it always be here for us to return, our beacon in the darkness.$B$BWe Wildhammer will forever call Grim Batol our ancestral home.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO `locales_page_text` VALUES (50679, '$n, I\'ve seen how you handle your weapon and I must say - you show potential.$B$BWith a bit of training, we should be able to rough you up into a workable shape! Who knows, maybe you\'ll become a bruiser in the end, or even one of those adventurous types running around all of Azeroth. Whatever it will be, with enough money I can give you a nice headstart for your future career.$B$BGizzie the Enforcer, Warrior Trainer.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO `locales_page_text` VALUES (50680, '$n, news goes around Rustgate Ridge that some big shot prodigy mage blasts their way through the coalpits.$B$BArcane power is cool and all that, but unrefined abilities won\'t bring you any gold. And it will make us look like amateurs too in turn. Should you ever desire to hone your magical skills to something more profitable, give me a holler up in Rustgate\'s Tower. Don\'t forget to bring some coin, my dear!$B$BWizette Icewhistle, Mage Trainer.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO `locales_page_text` VALUES (50681, '$n, I heard the beautiful BOOMS coming down from the coalpits. Figured it must be you, the others had pitiful booms, quite boring, too.$B$BInterested in learning how to make even bigger booms with different kinds of tricks and shots? I can teach you a few things to help you against the wildlife around here, and who knows, maybe you\'ll have your own pet one day! Just holler at me and I\'ll cover everything you need.$B$BMayten Boomrifle, Hunter Trainer.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO `locales_page_text` VALUES (50682, '$n, rumours spread of a particularly agile goblin doing menial tasks in the coalpits. If you ask me, you\'re destined for more.$B$BA rogue has many abilities that suit us goblins - our subtlety, nimble fingers and general willingness to overlook morals are perfect requisites. If you are interested in catching a few new tricks on how to get money, then I\'ll be happy to oblige - with the right payment, ofcourse.$B$BLeyli Quicktongue, Rogue Trainer.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO `locales_page_text` VALUES (50683, '$n, the shadows have a certain allure, don\'t they? I\'ve seen you flinging bolts left and right and you seem to be a promising individual!$B$BIn this world, the unassuming are the ones with the most advantages. Use that, and power and gold will be in your lap faster than you can blink. Show me how eager you are to learn more about what a warlock is capable of by paying me and in turn I\'ll instruct you in the arts of demonology.$B$BAmri Demondeal, Warlock Trainer.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
